data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER !!! Come see this unique  4 bedroom 2.5 bath home located in the infamous Dolphin Bay Bayfront gated community. This home has a beautiful screened in pool with privacy fence in the back yard. Seller has just recently had the front yard laid with fresh sod! Dolphin Bay is a private, gated, family-oriented community nestled alongside scenic St. Andrews Bay in beautiful Panama City Beach, Florida. The pet friendly community, located only minutes away from the nation's most beautiful beaches and the area's best entertainment and shopping, has a small-town feel and offers such amenities as a marina, tennis/pickle-ball/basketball court and beautifully landscaped pocket parks. Dont let this one slip away. Call your favorite agent today and schedule a showing before its gone
